'''圣尼古拉堂'''（St Nicholas Church）是一座已废弃的历史教堂，位于英格兰[[格洛斯特|格洛斯特]]西门街<ref name="cct">[https://www.visitchurches.org.uk/visit/church-listing/st-nicholas-gloucester.html] {{Wayback|url=https://www.visitchurches.org.uk/visit/church-listing/st-nicholas-gloucester.html |date=20201126002543 }}{{Citation|title=St Nicholas' Church, Gloucester, Gloucestershire|url=https://www.visitchurches.org.uk/visit/church-listing/st-nicholas-gloucester.html|publisher=Churches Conservation Trust|accessdate=2020-11-28|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126002543/https://www.visitchurches.org.uk/visit/church-listing/st-nicholas-gloucester.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，已列为I级[[登录建筑|登录建筑]].<ref name="hg">{{NHLE |num= 1245083|desc= Church of St Nicholas, Gloucester|accessdate= 7 April 2015|mode=cs2}}</ref>。其尖顶是市中心的地标之一<ref name=bex/>。

==历史==
该堂创建于1190年前后<ref name=bex>{{Citation| url = http://www.britainexpress.com/attractions.htm?attraction=4208| title = Gloucester, St Nicholas Church| access-date = 30 September 2010| publisher = Britain Express| archive-date = 2021-01-15| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210115152459/https://www.britainexpress.com/attractions.htm?attraction=4208| dead-url = no}}</ref>，13世纪重建。15世纪增加西侧钟楼。<ref name=hg/> 尖顶最初高 {{convert|200|ft|m|0}}。<ref>{{Citation| url = http://www.britannia.com/history/glos/churches/glosstnic.html| title = Churches of Gloucester: St Nicholas, Gloucester| access-date = 30 September 2010| publisher = Britannia.com| archive-date = 2012-09-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120918002706/http://www.britannia.com/history/glos/churches/glosstnic.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>1783年降低高度<ref name=hg/>。在16世纪，曾是该城最富有的堂区。<ref>{{citation|url= http://www.british-history.ac.uk/report.aspx?compid=42278|title= The City of Gloucester: Medieval Gloucester|access-date= 30 September 2010|editor1-last= Herbert|editor1-first= N. M.|work= A History of the County of Gloucester|volume= 4|year= 1988|series= Victoria County History|publisher= University of London & History of Parliament Trust|pages= 63–72|archive-date= 2014-09-02|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140902220052/http://www.british-history.ac.uk/report.aspx?compid=42278|dead-url= no}}</ref>  1967年教堂关闭<ref>Jurica, John. ''Gloucester A Pictorial History''. Chichester: Phillimore, 1994, caption 76. {{ISBN|0-85033-836-0}}</ref> 1971年5月7日宣布废弃，1975年6月25日交给教堂保护信托基金会。<ref>{{Citation| year = 2011| title = Diocese of Gloucester: All Schemes| series = Church Commissioners/Statistics| publisher = [[Church_of_England|Church of England]]| page = 3| format = PDF| url = http://www.churchofengland.org/media/810623/gloucester%20-%20all%20schemes.pdf| access-date = 11 April 2011| archive-date = 2016-03-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306185640/https://www.churchofengland.org/media/810623/gloucester%20-%20all%20schemes.pdf| dead-url = no}}</ref>

